These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pomegranate, kale, grapes
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, folk, pop, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, australian, polish, french
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, bird, snake
 1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
 3. the canadian is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 5. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the australian is the person eating kale##1
 8. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the snake and the fan of soul##2
10. the person eating asparagus is the owner of the snake##1
11. the fan of pop is the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | kale  | asparagus    | grapes    | pomegranate   |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | gospel   | pop       | soul    |
| Nationality   | australian | canadian | french    | polish |
| Pet           | dog | snake       | guinea-pig | bird     |

