.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, radish, raspberry, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing, puzzles, hiking
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, british, german, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, parkour, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 2. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 4. the person eating radish is the japanese##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the japanese is on the left or right of the german##3
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 9. the german is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
11. the german is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | watermelon  | radish    | raspberry     | onion       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | hiking | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | german | japanese   | british   | brazilian    |
| Sport         | parkour | water-polo  | golf | handball   |

