.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, lemonade, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, analyst, nurse, firefighter
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, polish, dutch, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, pony, horse
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 2. the polish is the nurse##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the fisherman is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the firefighter##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the malaysian##1
 8. the firefighter is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the indian##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk | lemonade   | fanta    | iced-tea      |
| Job           | nurse | fisherman | analyst | firefighter     |
| Nationality   | polish      | malaysian   | indian   | dutch |
| Pet           | horse         | chinchilla       | pony  | snake       |

