.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, lemonade, cola
There 4 different types of food: kale, garlic, asparagus, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, reading, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, baseball, snowboarding
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating kale##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating peas##1
12. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | cola       | lemonade   | mirinda   | tea   |
| Food       | garlic        | peas | kale    | asparagus       |
| Hobby      | fishing | hiking    | reading  | singing |
| Sport      | weightlifting  | baseball  | basketball | snowboarding    |

