.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, mango, pear, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, woodworking, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, photographer, designer, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, volleyball, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's sport is handball and the person eating papaya##2
 3. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the photographer is the person eating grapefruit##1
 5. the accountant is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating mango is the accountant##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the photographer##1
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
10. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pear    | papaya      | grapefruit          | mango    |
| Hobby   | dancing | chess       | woodworking | video-games |
| Job     | chef     | designer      | photographer     | accountant |
| Sport   | rowing   | rugby | volleyball        | handball   |

