.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, fanta
There 4 different types of food: radish, avocado, spinach, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, d&b, indie, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, australian, egyptian, mexican
 1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of trance is between the egyptian and the fan of d&b##2
 7. the fan of indie is the person eating spinach##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is the person eating spinach##1
 9. the australian is on the far right##1
10. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | sprite    | almond-milk       | fanta       |
| Food          | asparagus    | spinach | avocado | radish     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | indie        | trance    | d&b   |
| Nationality   | italian  | egyptian      | mexican    | australian |

