 3. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the project-manager##2
 5. the person eating artichoke is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
