 9. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
12. the lawyer is on the left or right of the librarian##3
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

