.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, chess, rock-climbing, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, comedy, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, snowboarding, cricket
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | coffee | soy-milk        | almond-milk        |
| Hobby         | reading | rock-climbing       | hiking | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster        | epic    | comedy      |
| Sport         | surfing     | snowboarding    | cricket | rowing   |

