.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, folk, blues, country
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, thai, egyptian, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, badminton, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, airplane, snowmobile
 1. the fan of country is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the spanish and the colombian##2
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the thai##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the colombian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
10. the spanish is in an even position##4
11. the spanish is on the far right##1
12. the fan of metal is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | metal | country     | blues        |
| Nationality   | egyptian | colombian  | thai     | spanish |
| Sport         | baseball    | cricket | badminton      | volleyball |
| Transport     | snowmobile | motorbike     | airplane | boat       |

 